\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:15:\"Daniel Kossmann\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5621:\"\n<p>No dia 11 de maio de 2019 aconteceu o evento global <a href=\"https://wptranslationday.org/\">WordPress Translation Day 4</a> e a comunidade brasileira marcou presen√ßa tanto com duas palestras virtuais, quanto com <a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/2019/05/09/wordpress-translation-day-4/\">quatro encontros presenciais</a> em <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpsampa/events/260963644/\">S√£o Paulo</a>, <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Meetup-de-WordPress-Balneario-Camboriu/events/261024142/\">Balne√°rio Cambori√∫</a>, <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/Blumenau-WordPress-Meetup/events/261015137/\">Blumenau</a> e <a href=\"https://www.meetup.com/pt-BR/wpcuritiba/events/260729102/\">Curitiba</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Durante os encontros foram realizados workshops sobre como ajudar na tradu√ß√£o do WordPress e tamb√©m foi colocada a m√£o na massa realizando tradu√ß√µes.</p>\n\n\n\n<span id=\"more-1534\"></span>\n\n\n\n<h2>Resumo das atividades</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Segue abaixo os itens que receberam colabora√ß√µes na tradu√ß√£o.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>Temas</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/themes/envince/\">Envince</a>;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Plugins</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/plugins/church-admin/\">Church Admin</a>; </li><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/plugins/contact-form-7/\">Contact Form 7</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/plugins/shareadraft/\">Share a Draft</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/plugins/public-post-preview/\">Public Post Preview</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/plugins/autoptimize/\">Autoptimize</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/masks-form-fields/\">Masks Form Fields</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/amp-wp/\">AMP WP ‚Äì Google AMP For WordPress</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/pods-seo/\">Pods SEO</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/pdf-viewer-block/\">Gutenberg PDF Viewer Block;</a></li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/responsive-styled-google-maps-simplified/\">Responsive Styled Google Maps Simplified</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-super-cache/\">WP Super Cache</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/photo-gallery/\">Photo Gallery by 10Web ‚Äì Mobile-Friendly Image Gallery</a>;</li><li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-jetpack/\">Booster for WooCommerce</a>.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3>Outros</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Tradu√ß√£o dos <a href=\"https://apps.wordpress.com/mobile/\">aplicativos mobile para iOS e Android</a>;</li><li>Atualiza√ß√£o do Gloss√°rio e do Guia de Tradu√ß√£o;</li><li>Verifica√ß√£o e aprova√ß√£o de solicita√ß√µes de PTE;</li><li>Palestra virtual: <a href=\"https://www.crowdcast.io/e/wptranslationday4/20\">Dionizio Bach &#8211; The power of translation communities for business</a>;</li><li>Palestra virtual: <a href=\"https://www.crowdcast.io/e/wptranslationday4/21\">Felipe Elia &#8211; Traduzindo o WordPress em portugu√™s do Brasil</a>;</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>Voc√™ colaborou na tradu√ß√£o de algum projeto no WordPress Translation Day 4 que n√£o foi listado acima? Envie o link para n√≥s.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Fotos dos encontros</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery aligncenter columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wordpress-translation-day-4-sao-paulo.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://br.wordpress.org/files/2019/05/wordpress-translation-day-4-sao-paulo.jpeg\" alt=\"WordPress Translation Day 4 em S√£o Paulo\" data-id=\"1537\" data-link=\"https://br.wordpress.org/?attachment_id=1537\" class=\"wp-image-1537\" srcset=\"https